@startuml
title UC03 Credential user が user code で device flow を完了する

actor "Credential user" as User
participant "Client application" as Client
participant "Enki Gate UI" as UI
participant "Enki Gate API" as API
database "Firestore" as Firestore
participant "Cloud Logging" as Logging

Client -> API: device flow を開始
API -> Firestore: device flow を作成
Firestore --> API: deviceCode / userCode
API --> Client: deviceCode / userCode / verification URI

User -> UI: Enki Gate の device flow 画面を開く
UI --> User: Google ログインを促す
User -> UI: Google でログイン
User -> UI: user code を入力
UI -> API: user code の検証を要求
API -> Firestore: device flow を検索
Firestore --> API: device flow 状態
API --> UI: user code の検証結果
UI -> Firestore: 認証済みユーザーとして利用可能 credential を取得
Firestore --> UI: 選択可能な credential 一覧
UI --> User: credential 一覧を表示

User -> UI: 利用する credential を選択
UI -> API: device flow 完了を要求
API -> Firestore: device flow を authorized に更新
Firestore --> API: 記録完了
API -> Logging: device flow 完了を記録
API --> UI: 完了結果を返す
UI --> User: 利用開始完了を表示

loop polling
  Client -> API: device flow 状態を確認
  API -> Firestore: device flow を確認
  Firestore --> API: pending または authorized

  alt pending
    API --> Client: pending
  else authorized
    API -> Firestore: token issuance を記録
    Firestore --> API: 記録完了
    API -> Firestore: device flow を completed に更新
    Firestore --> API: 更新完了
    API -> Logging: token 発行を記録
    API --> Client: gateway token を返す
  end
end
@enduml
